#: src/live2d-Login.php:137
msgid "如果您发现登录没有反应，或者出现了错误，请先检查 <a href=\"%1$s\">%1$s</a> 是否可以被访问"
msgstr "If sign-in does not respond or returns an error, please first check whether <a href=\"%1$s\">%1$s</a> is reachable."

#: src/live2d-Login.php:151
