#: src/live2d-Utils.php:92
msgid "V1 / V2 模型"
msgstr "V1 vs. V2 models"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:94
msgid "本插件同时支持两套独立的 Live2D 加载链路。第一次配置前请先确认手里的模型属于哪一类："
msgstr "This plugin ships two completely independent Live2D loaders. Before your first configuration, decide which one your model belongs to:"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:96
msgid "模型类别"
msgstr "Category"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:97
msgid "清单文件"
msgstr "Manifest file"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:98
msgid "主体文件"
msgstr "Main file"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:99
msgid "对应 API 方式"
msgstr "Matching API mode"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:101
msgid "V1（Cubism 2 / 3 系，如 22 娘、Pio、Tia、Shizuku 等）"
msgstr "V1 (Cubism 2 / 3 era — 22-Niang, Pio, Tia, Shizuku, etc.)"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:103
msgid "「本地部署旧版模型」或「自行部署旧版模型」"
msgstr "\"Local legacy models\" or \"Self-hosted legacy models\""

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:104
msgid "Cubism 4+（V2，官方仍在维护的最新格式）"
msgstr "Cubism 4+ (V2 — the format Live2D Inc. is actively maintaining)"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:106
msgid "「自定义新版模型 · 直链加载」或「自定义新版模型 · 托管到本站」(均需登录并购买授权)"
msgstr "\"Custom Cubism 4+ model · Direct link\" or \"Custom Cubism 4+ model · Host on this site\" (both require sign-in and a purchased license)"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:108
msgid "简单判断：清单文件名以 .model3.json 结尾就是 V2，否则是 V1。"
msgstr "Quick check: if the manifest filename ends with .model3.json it is V2, otherwise it is V1."

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:115
msgid "API 方式与模型路径"
msgstr "API mode and model path"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:117
msgid "「API 方式」是 V1 / V2 链路的总开关, 2026-05 重构后由原三选项 + protectV2 二态合并为「四选项 radio」, 每个选项作用不同:"
msgstr "\"API mode\" is the master switch for the V1 / V2 pipeline. After the 2026-05 refactor, the original 3 options + protectV2 toggle were merged into a single 4-option radio. Each option behaves differently:"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:119
#: src/waifu-Settings-Base.php:148
msgid "本地部署旧版模型"
msgstr "Local legacy models"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:119
msgid "使用插件随包内置的 V1 模型, 由本站 REST 接口 (/wp-json/live2d/v1/model/*) 提供, 不向外网发起请求。「模型 ID」「材质 ID」会自动变成下拉框。需要在「Live 2D 创意工坊」页面先把模型下载到本地。"
msgstr "Uses the V1 models bundled with the plugin, served via this site's REST API (/wp-json/live2d/v1/model/*). No outbound network calls. \"Model ID\" and \"Texture ID\" automatically become dropdowns. The model must first be downloaded from the \"Live 2D Workshop\" page."

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:120
#: src/waifu-Settings-Base.php:157
msgid "自行部署旧版模型"
msgstr "Self-hosted legacy models"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:120
msgid "对接您自己服务器或第三方提供的 V1 模型 API (即 fghrsh 风格接口), 「模型 API」需要填写返回 model_list.json 的接口根地址。"
msgstr "Talks to a V1 model API hosted by you or a third party (i.e. the fghrsh-style API). The \"Model API\" field must be set to the root URL that returns model_list.json."

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:121
msgid "自定义新版模型 · 直链加载 (Cubism 4+)"
msgstr "Custom Cubism 4+ model · Direct link"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:121
msgid "用于 Cubism 4+ 模型 (V2, *.model3.json), 「模型 API」填跨域 URL, 浏览器直接拉源站。需登录账号并完成付费后才能选择, 防盗链由对象存储 / CDN 站长自己处理。"
msgstr "For Cubism 4+ models (V2, *.model3.json). \"Model API\" takes a cross-origin URL and the browser fetches the origin directly. Available only after sign-in and payment; hotlink protection is handled by you on the object storage / CDN side."

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:122
msgid "自定义新版模型 · 托管到本站 (Cubism 4+, 推荐)"
msgstr "Custom Cubism 4+ model · Host on this site (recommended)"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:122
msgid "同上, 但插件会把模型下载 / 托管到本站 wp-content/plugins/live-2d/model/{slug}/, 并代为防盗链 (临时签名 URL)。需登录账号并完成付费后才能选择。"
msgstr "Same as above, but the plugin downloads / hosts the model under wp-content/plugins/live-2d/model/{slug}/ on this site and handles hotlink protection for you (short-lived signed URLs). Available only after sign-in and payment."

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:124
msgid "选了「托管到本站」后的表单变化"
msgstr "Form changes after selecting \"Host on this site\""

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:125
msgid "选「自定义新版模型 · 托管到本站」后, 「模型 API」输入框会被隐藏, 系统自动把它写成本站 wp-content/plugins/live-2d/model/ 根地址。站长唯一需要填的是「模型目录」列表, 每行一个 slug (= 子目录名), 插件会按 {root}{slug}/{slug}.model3.json 自动展开为完整 manifest URL。"
msgstr "After choosing \"Custom Cubism 4+ model · Host on this site\", the \"Model API\" input is hidden and the system automatically points it at this site's wp-content/plugins/live-2d/model/ root. The only thing you need to fill in is the \"Model directory\" list - one slug (= subfolder name) per line; the plugin expands it to a full manifest URL as {root}{slug}/{slug}.model3.json."

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:126
msgid "「模型 API」何时以 .json 结尾、何时以斜杠结尾"
msgstr "When \"Model API\" should end with .json vs. with a trailing slash"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:127
msgid "仅当「API 方式 = 自定义新版模型 · 直链加载」时, 「模型 API」支持以下两种写法, 由结尾字符决定走哪种:"
msgstr "Only when \"API mode = Custom Cubism 4+ model · Direct link\", the \"Model API\" field supports two forms, distinguished by the trailing character:"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:129
msgid "写法"
msgstr "Format"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:130
msgid "行为"
msgstr "Behaviour"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:131
msgid "「模型目录」是否使用"
msgstr "Is \"Model directory\" used?"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:133
msgid "以 .json 结尾 (直链单模型)"
msgstr "Ends with .json (single direct-link model)"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:134
msgid "直接当作 *.model3.json 加载, 不再做任何路径拼接。例: https://cdn.example.com/live2d/haru/haru.model3.json"
msgstr "Loaded as *.model3.json directly with no path concatenation. Example: https://cdn.example.com/live2d/haru/haru.model3.json"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:135
msgid "忽略, 下方「模型目录」「待机动画文件名」两行会自动隐藏。"
msgstr "Ignored. The \"Model directory\" and \"Idle motion file name\" rows below are auto-hidden."

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:136
msgid "以 / 结尾 (目录根 + 多模型)"
msgstr "Ends with / (directory root + multiple models)"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:137
msgid "当作根目录使用, 配合下方「模型目录」每行一个 slug, 自动按 {模型 API}{slug}/{slug}.model3.json 拼成完整 URL。"
msgstr "Treated as a directory root. Combined with the \"Model directory\" list below (one slug per line), full URLs are auto-built as {Model API}{slug}/{slug}.model3.json."

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:138
msgid "必填。每行写一个子目录名称, 名称必须与 {slug}.model3.json 的前缀完全一致。"
msgstr "Required. One subfolder name per line; the name must exactly match the {slug}.model3.json prefix."

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:140
msgid "补充约束: 路径不能包含中文; HTTPS 站点的模型清单及其引用到的所有资源 (.moc3、贴图、motion3.json、physics3.json 等) 也必须是 HTTPS; 放在第三方对象存储 / CDN 时请正确开启 CORS。"
msgstr "Additional constraints: paths must not contain CJK characters; on HTTPS sites, the model manifest and every asset it references (.moc3, textures, motion3.json, physics3.json, etc.) must also be HTTPS; when hosted on third-party object storage / CDN, make sure CORS is enabled correctly."

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:141
msgid "「默认材质 ID」仅 V1 模型使用, V2 模型留空即可。"
msgstr "\"Default texture ID\" applies only to V1 models. Leave it empty for V2 models."

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:148
msgid "模型防盗保护 (Cubism 4+)"
msgstr "Model hotlink protection (Cubism 4+)"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:150
msgid "防盗链只对 Cubism 4+ 模型的两个「自定义新版模型」选项生效; 旧版 V1 走本站 REST 接口, 不需要这层保护。"
msgstr "Hotlink protection only applies to the two \"Custom Cubism 4+ model\" options. Legacy V1 goes through this site's REST API and doesn't need this layer."

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:152
msgid "自定义新版模型 · 直链加载"
msgstr "Custom Cubism 4+ model · Direct link"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:152
msgid "插件不动您填的「模型 API」, 浏览器直接拉源站。适用于您已经把模型放在阿里云 OSS、腾讯云 COS、又拍、七牛、自家 CDN 等已经具备 Referer 防盗 / URL 鉴权能力的存储上 (原 protectV2 = direct)。"
msgstr "The plugin leaves your \"Model API\" untouched and the browser fetches the origin directly. Suitable when the model is hosted on storage that already supports Referer-based hotlink protection / URL signing - e.g. Aliyun OSS, Tencent COS, Upyun, Qiniu, your own CDN (formerly protectV2 = direct)."

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:153
msgid "自定义新版模型 · 托管到本站 (推荐)"
msgstr "Custom Cubism 4+ model · Host on this site (recommended)"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:153
msgid "插件会把模型文件保存到本站 wp-content/plugins/live-2d/model/{slug}/, 并对前端只露出经过签名的临时 URL, 访客 F12 也看不到源站地址。适用于源站没有防盗能力 (GitHub Pages、jsDelivr、自建 nginx 等) (原 protectV2 = local)。"
msgstr "The plugin saves model files to this site's wp-content/plugins/live-2d/model/{slug}/ and only exposes signed short-lived URLs to the frontend; visitors using DevTools can't see the origin address. Suitable when the origin lacks hotlink protection (GitHub Pages, jsDelivr, self-hosted nginx, etc.) (formerly protectV2 = local)."

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:155
msgid "选「托管到本站」后, 「模型 API」输入框会被隐藏, 系统自动写成本站 model/ 根地址; 站长唯一需要填的是「模型目录」列表 (每行一个 slug)。页面下方会出现「模型托管」面板, 含双标签页: 从 URL 下载 / 上传文件夹。两者完成后都会自动把 slug 追加到「模型目录」列表, 点「保存设置」后生效。"
msgstr "After choosing \"Host on this site\", the \"Model API\" input is hidden and the system writes this site's model/ root automatically. The only thing you need to fill is the \"Model directory\" list (one slug per line). A \"Model hosting\" panel appears at the bottom with two tabs: Download from URL / Upload folder. After either action the slug is appended to the \"Model directory\" list automatically; click \"Save settings\" to apply."

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:156
msgid "2026-05 后取消了访客首次访问时的「自动懒下载」 (原为默认行为但不可见, 需要站长主动点「下载到本站」或拖拽上传。「清理孤儿」用于删除已经从设置里移除、但还残留在本地缓存里的旧模型文件。"
msgstr "Since 2026-05, the implicit \"lazy download on first visit\" behavior was removed (it used to be the default but was not visible). The site owner must now explicitly click \"Download to this site\" or drag-and-drop an upload. \"Clean orphans\" is used to delete old model files that were removed from settings but still linger in the local cache."

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:163
msgid "提示消息与特殊标记"
msgstr "Tip messages and placeholders"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:167
msgid "在「高级设置」「提示消息选项」页面点击 %s 可以在同一个事件下追加随机语句，运行时随机选一条显示。"
msgstr "In the \"Advanced settings\" or \"Tip message options\" page, click %s to add another random sentence to the same event; one of them is picked at random at runtime."

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:170
msgid "以下事件支持在文本中插入特殊标记，运行时会被替换为对应内容："
msgstr "These events support placeholders that get replaced at runtime:"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:172
msgid "鼠标悬停时的消息提示：{text} 触发事件的内容、{highlight} 高亮样式占位符"
msgstr "Mouse hover tip: {text} the triggering content, {highlight} the highlight-style placeholder"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:173
msgid "鼠标点击时的消息提示：{text} 触发事件的内容、{highlight} 高亮样式占位符"
msgstr "Mouse click tip: {text} the triggering content, {highlight} the highlight-style placeholder"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:174
msgid "节日事件：{year} 年份、{highlight} 高亮样式占位符"
msgstr "Holiday events: {year} the year, {highlight} the highlight-style placeholder"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:175
msgid "搜索引擎入站提示：{title} 网站标题、{keyword} 关键词、{website} 站点名称、{highlight} 高亮样式占位符（请以预设值为准，并非所有搜索引擎都会带齐这些信息）"
msgstr "Search-engine referral tip: {title} page title, {keyword} keyword, {website} site name, {highlight} highlight-style placeholder (refer to the defaults — not every search engine provides all of these)."

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:176
msgid "访问本站点的提示：{website} 站点名称、{highlight} 高亮样式占位符"
msgstr "Site visitor tip: {website} site name, {highlight} highlight-style placeholder"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:177
msgid "一言 API 的消息：{title}、{source}、{creator}、{date}、{dynasty}、{author}、{highlight}（请以预设值为准，并非所有句子都会带齐这些字段）"
msgstr "Hitokoto API message: {title}, {source}, {creator}, {date}, {dynasty}, {author}, {highlight} (refer to the defaults — not every sentence carries all of these fields)."

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:181
msgid "高亮用法：在任意 style 属性中插入 %s 即可，高亮颜色请到「提示消息选项」中设置。"
msgstr "Highlight usage: insert %s into any style attribute; the highlight colour is configured under \"Tip message options\"."

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:184
msgid "如需恢复全部默认值：删除插件后重新安装即可（注意会同时清空已保存的设置）。"
msgstr "To restore every default: uninstall and reinstall the plugin (this also wipes your saved settings)."

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:191
msgid "样式与工具栏"
msgstr "Style and toolbar"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:194
msgid "「看板娘大小」「页面边距」「拖拽样式」位于「样式设置」页，调整后立即对前端生效。"
msgstr "\"Waifu size\", \"Page padding\" and \"Drag mode\" live on the \"Style settings\" page — changes take effect on the front end immediately."

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:195
msgid "「面页小于指定宽度禁用看板娘」用于在小屏 / 移动端隐藏，留空或填 0 表示始终显示。"
msgstr "\"Hide waifu when the page is narrower than\" hides the waifu on small screens / mobile devices; leave it empty or set 0 to always display."

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:196
msgid "「模型切换方式」「材质切换方式」分别决定按下工具栏切换按钮时是顺序切换还是随机切换。"
msgstr "\"Model switch mode\" and \"Texture switch mode\" decide whether the toolbar buttons cycle sequentially or pick at random."

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:197
msgid "「超采样」与「抗锯齿」属于付费功能，仅对 V2 模型有效，开启后可显著提升贴图清晰度，但会增加 GPU 占用。"
