#: src/live2d-Utils.php:237
msgid "已经在 live2dweb.com 完成账号登录，并把账号 Key 保存到「Live 2D 设置 → 登录」选项卡。"
msgstr "Signed in on live2dweb.com and saved your account Key under \"Live 2D Settings → Sign in\"."

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:238
msgid "已经完成邮箱验证（V1 模型下载本身不收费，但需要可联系到的邮箱以便接收授权变更通知）。"
msgstr "Verified your email address. (V1 downloads themselves are free, but a reachable email is needed for licence-change notifications.)"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:240
msgid "下载完成后，请前往「Live 2D 设置 → 基础设置」，把「API 方式」切换到「本地部署旧版模型」，然后在「默认模型 ID」下拉中即可看到刚才下载的模型并选用。"
msgstr "After downloading, open \"Live 2D Settings → General settings\", switch \"API mode\" to \"Local legacy models\", and the model you just downloaded will be selectable from the \"Default model ID\" dropdown."

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:241
msgid "如果某个模型下载失败：先确认 Key 仍然有效（登录页会提示），并检查站点是否能访问 download.live2dweb.com；网络环境受限的站点也可以在源站手动下载 ZIP 后放进 wp-content/plugins/live-2d/model/ 目录。"
msgstr "If a download fails: first confirm your Key is still valid (the sign-in page will warn), then check that your server can reach download.live2dweb.com. Sites with restricted network access can also fetch the ZIP manually from the origin and drop it into wp-content/plugins/live-2d/model/."

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:242
msgid "Cubism 4+ 模型不会出现在本页面，需要在「Live 2D 设置 → 基础设置」选择「自定义新版模型 · 直链加载」或「自定义新版模型 · 托管到本站」后自行填写 model3.json 地址(直链)或在「模型目录」每行填一个 slug(托管到本站),并参考「设置帮助 → API 方式与模型路径」一节。"
msgstr "Cubism 4+ models do not appear on this page. In \"Live 2D Settings → Base settings\", pick \"Custom Cubism 4+ model · Direct link\" or \"Custom Cubism 4+ model · Host on this site\", then either fill in the model3.json URL (direct link) or add one slug per line under \"Model directory\" (host on this site). See the \"Settings help → API mode and model path\" section for details."

